additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Fresh Milk, Sugar, Fresh Cream (14%), Milk Solids, Cocoa Solids, Water, Wheat Flour, Maltodextrin, Vegetable Oil, Emulsifiers (471, 476, 477 - Soy), Glucose, Butter (Soy Lecithin), Thickeners (Guar Gum, Carrageenan), Raising Agents (Sodium Bicarbonate, 503), Tapioca Syrup, Flavours, Salt, Corn Starch, Acidity Regulator (Tocopherols Concentrate), Colours (Caramel IV Annatto), Contains no less than 10% Milk Fat in Ice Cream, Contains 27% Cocoa Solids in White Chocolate

additionalProperty.name: Allergen
additionalProperty.value: Contains Soybean, May Contain Egg, Contains Gluten, May Contain Peanuts, Contains Wheat, May Contain Tree Nuts, Contains Milk

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Broken sticks rarely occur but may cause a choking or injury hazard. Adult supervision recommended for children 0-5 years.
